<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idcc301045-47c4-11f1-9671-b5c725212f70"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior section 44931, <ref href="/us/pl/103/272/s1/e">Pub. L. 103–272, § 1(e)</ref>, <date date="1994-07-05">July 5, 1994</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/108/1215">108 Stat. 1215</ref>, related to the Director of Intelligence and Security, prior to repeal by <ref href="/us/pl/107/71/tI/s101/f/6">Pub. L. 107–71, title I, § 101(f)(6)</ref>, <date date="2001-11-19">Nov. 19, 2001</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/115/603">115 Stat. 603</ref>.</p>
